comment: Winslow (MIA) sets the screen on Lowry (TOR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Lowry (TOR) makes incidental contact with Wade (MIA) that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Wade (MIA) makes body contact with DeRozan (TOR) that affects his RSBQ.
Joseph (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position with Wade (MIA) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Lowry (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Dragic (MIA).
[Observable in enhanced video] Dragic (MIA) gathers the ball and slides his pivot foot as he comes to a stop.
Joseph (TOR) makes incidental contact with Wade (MIA) that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Biyombo (TOR) hooks Winslow (MIA) while under the rim.
Joseph (TOR) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Wade's (MIA) shot attempt.
Biyombo (TOR) makes contact with the ball after it has reached its apex and is on its downward flight toward the basket.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the goaltending call on the court is upheld.
Dragic (MIA) and Joseph (TOR) engage briefly before the timeout is called.
Johnson (MIA) and DeRozan (TOR) engage briefly before the timeout is called.
Green (MIA) and DeRozan (TOR) briefly engage and separate prior to the inbound pass.
Green (MIA) commits a take foul on DeRozan (TOR).
Joseph (TOR) makes incidental contact with Wade (MIA) that does not affect his FOM Off Ball. R-Slash appears to show Wade trip over Dragic (MIA) as he attempts to squeeze through a congested area.
Dragic (MIA) commits a take foul on DeRozan (TOR).
